STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Shannon Christopher TURNER, Defendant-Appellant. No. 18-1599 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed April 17, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Shannon Turner appeals his sentence after pleading guilty to operating while intoxicated and assault with intent to commit sexual abuse. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
